580
00:43:15,240 --> 00:43:16,560
Harper's regular-expression matcher

581
00:43:16,560 --> 00:43:18,520
is a continuation-based algorithm

582
00:43:18,520 --> 00:43:20,240
for regular-expression matching,

583
00:43:20,240 --> 00:43:23,600
