611
00:44:20,720 --> 00:44:22,720
in a little bit, but to
start off in Haskell,

612
00:44:22,720 --> 00:44:24,800
so, it's a continuation-based
algorithm.

613
00:44:24,800 --> 00:44:27,160
So, we have a type K
for continuations.

